messages.message:
[Week 3 of Cypress merge-blocking (May 20-May 23). Here are the stats of Cypress runs on CI
# of test runs: 219
# of test canceled/timed out: 41 + 2 = 43
# of test failed/errored runs: 124
# fo test passed: 52
Failure rate: 124 / (219 - 43) = 70.45*%*
fwiw a decent amount of these failures are due to crafting i think
Yeah all the tests were failing for half of the week because of the deployment issues
Yes, just keep track of the overall failure rate. Every commit has a 70% chance to fail in Cypress Ci
